                <div class="row align-items-center justify-content-center">
                    <div class="col-xl-7 col-lg-8">
                        <div class="tg-video-img wow fadeInLeft" data-wow-delay=".2s">
                            <Image src={videoBg} alt="" />
                            <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=USeAeVaVV0k" class="play-btn popup-video" aria-label="button play"> <i class="fas fa-play"></i></a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-xl-5 col-lg-8">
                        <div class="tg-video-content wow fadeInRight" data-wow-delay=".2s">
                            <div class="tg-section-title white mb-30">
                                <span class="sub-title">Lihat Cara Kerjanya</span>
                                <h2 class="title white-text" aria-label="cara tepat menggunakan veromance serum">Cara Tepat Menggunakan Veromance Serum</h2>
                            </div>
                            <p class="info-one">Dapatkan hasil maksimal dari produk kami. Tonton video singkat ini untuk melihat langkah-langkah penggunaan yang benar agar pengalaman Anda lebih nyaman dan efektif.</p>
                            <p class="info-two">Temukan tips dan trik eksklusif dari para ahli kami untuk meningkatkan rutinitas perawatan diri Anda.</p>
                            <a href="#product" class="tg-btn">Beli Sekarang</a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
        <section id="product" class="tg-shop-area pt-100 pb-60">
            <div class="container">
                <div class="row justify-content-center">
                    <div class="col-lg-8">
                        <div class="tg-section-title text-center mb-60">
                            <span class="sub-title">KOLEKSI ANDALAN KAMI</span>
                            <h2 class="title">Temukan yang Paling Cocok Untukmu</h2>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="tg-shop-wrapper">
                    <div class="row justify-content-center">
                        <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-6 col-sm-9">
                            <div class="tg-shop-item text-center">
                                <div class="tg-shop-thumb">
                                    <span class="new" style="background-color: #ff4081; color: white;">Paling Laris</span>
                                    <a href="shop-details.html"><Image src={missbb} height={500} alt="Miss B&B Serum" /></a>
                                    <div class="tg-shop-action">
                                        <a href="/" aria-label="button shop" class="action-item"><i class="far fa-heart"></i></a>
                                        <a href="/" aria-label="button shop" class="action-item"><i class="flaticon-shopping-cart-1"></i></a>
                                        <a href="/" aria-label="button shop" class="action-item"><i class="flaticon-search"></i></a>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="tg-shop-content">
                                    <div class="tg-shop-cat">
                                        <a href="/">Perawatan Tubuh</a>
                                    </div>
                                    <h4 class="title"><a href="shop-details.html">Miss B&B Serum</a></h4>
                                    <div class="tg-shop-price">Rp 250.000</div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-6 col-sm-9">
                            <div class="tg-shop-item text-center">
                                <div class="tg-shop-thumb">
                                    <span class="new">Baru</span>
                                    <a href="shop-details.html"><Image src={vCare} height={500} alt="V-Care Feminine Hygiene" /></a>
                                    <div class="tg-shop-action">
                                        <a href="/" aria-label="button shop" class="action-item"><i class="far fa-heart"></i></a>
                                        <a href="/" aria-label="button shop" class="action-item"><i class="flaticon-shopping-cart-1"></i></a>
                                        <a href="/" aria-label="button shop" class="action-item"><i class="flaticon-search"></i></a>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="tg-shop-content">
                                    <div class="tg-shop-cat">
                                        <a href="/">Pembersih Kewanitaan</a>
                                    </div>
                                    <h4 class="title"><a href="shop-details.html">V-Care Feminine Hygiene</a></h4>
                                    <div class="tg-shop-price">Rp 150.000</div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-6 col-sm-9">
                            <div class="tg-shop-item text-center">
                                <div class="tg-shop-thumb text-center" style="position: relative; background-color: #f0f0f0;">
                                    <Image src={hiddenProduct} height={500} alt="Produk baru akan datang" class="mx-auto" style="opacity: 0.3;" />
                                    <div class="absolute inset-0 flex items-center justify-center" style="position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; bottom: 0; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;">
                                        <span class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-500">SEGERA HADIR</span>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="tg-shop-content">
                                    <div class="tg-shop-cat">
                                        <a href="/">Inovasi Baru</a>
                                    </div>
                                    <h4 class="title"><a href="/">Nantikan Produk Baru Kami</a></h4>
                                    <div class="tg-shop-price"></div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
        <section id="kenapa" class="tg-service-area">
            <div class="container">
                <div class="tg-service-inner">
                    <div class="row justify-content-center">
                        <div class="col-lg-8">
                            <div class="tg-section-title text-center mb-60">
                                <span class="sub-title">KENAPA MEMILIH VEROMANCE?</span>
